Class Car

seng201.team005.models.Purchasable
seng201.team005.models.Car
Direct Known Subclasses:
Entrant
public class Car extends Purchasable
Represents a car in the game, which is a purchasable item with various stats. Extends the Purchasable class to inherit common properties and methods for items that can be bought or sold.
